subject: HISTORY
text: Give the century, B.C. or A.D., of each of the following, indicate who or what each was, and say why each is important in history: The First Hague Conference, Hannibal, The First Crusade, The League of Schmalkalde, Socrates, Capture of the Bastille, Charles XII, Cardinal Richelieu, the beginning of the Great Schism of the Papacy, William the Lion.
